# Local Ghost preview

This theme is developed against a local Ghost instance. The active copy lives next to this repo:

`../ghost-local/content/themes/spazio-pitch-multi/`

After **any** theme work that should show in the browser (templates, partials, `assets/css`, `assets/js`, `assets/built`, images, etc.):

1. If `assets/css/index.css` or `assets/js/index.js` sources changed, run **`npm run build`** first.
2. Run **`npm run sync:ghost`** (rsyncs this directory into the Ghost themes folder, then **`ghost restart`** from `../ghost-local`).

Do not end a coding session that touched the theme without running sync + restart when the user previews on local Ghost, unless they explicitly opt out.
